Samuel Montagu, has been engaged in a series of disposals because of
pressure from its original Swedish shareholders, many of which have gone
into receivership, to realise the cash.
Goschalk, 40, trained as a chartered accountant with Touche Ross; after
spells at London Trust and Chartfield, the venture capital group, he joined
